Package com.c2g4.SingHealthWebApp.Admin.Report

Class ReportEntry

java.lang.Object
com.c2g4.SingHealthWebApp.Admin.Report.ReportEntry
@Component
public class ReportEntry
extends java.lang.Object
ReportEntry is a representation of an entry of Report used for manipulation. Entries are never modified or deleted, only added and entries with the same qn_id essentially "overrule" older entries with the same qn_id.
Author:
LunarFox
